'''[[BYD Company|BYD]] Home Energy System''', simplified as '''[[BYD Company|BYD]] HES''', is an energy solution without any emission offered by the Chinese [[BYD Auto|auto]], [[BYD e6#Batteries and powertrain|battery]], [[Photovoltaics|PV]] manufacturer [[BYD Company|BYD]], integrating its internally developed components such as [[Photovoltaics|solar panel]], [[Iron phosphate]] [[BYD e6#Batteries and powertrain|battery]], [[inverter]] etc.<ref>[http://www.b2match.eu/icci2012/participants/96 ICCI2012]</ref><ref>[http://www.solarmyworld.com.au/home-energy-system.php SolarMyWorld]</ref> Briefly speaking, this system generates electricity from [[solar power]], and then stores it for whole day’s family energy use,<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://inverterphilippines.com/blog/2012/09/09/off-grid-inverters-byd-solar-home-energy-system-hes-tibet-project-2/ |title=Off-Grid Inverters {{!}} BYD Solar Home Energy System (HES) Tibet Project |access-date= 2012-09-19 |archive-url= https://archive.is/20130126191713/http://inverterphilippines.com/blog/2012/09/09/off-grid-inverters-byd-solar-home-energy-system-hes-tibet-project-2/ |archive-date= 2013-01-26 |dead-url=yes |df= }}</ref> realizing a non-contamination, non-emission life style. In addition, [[BYD Company|BYD]]’s pronounced its customization service for different demands from consumers/clients.

Another significant function of [[BYD Company|BYD]] HES is the possibility of electric power feedback to the [[Electric grid|Grid]] when necessary.

[[BYD Company|BYD]] HES has ever made its appearance several times during professional symposiums like [[Solar power in the United States|Intersolar]] Europe, [[Solar Power International]] etc. and started its sales in Japan<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.autoinfo.gov.cn/autoinfo_eng/latest/webinfo/2011/07/1309140353747553.htm |title=BYD begins to sell household energy storage batteries in Japan |access-date=2012-09-19 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20121128031226/http://www.autoinfo.gov.cn/autoinfo_eng/latest/webinfo/2011/07/1309140353747553.htm |archive-date=2012-11-28 |dead-url=yes |df= }}</ref> and some other regions, but no more official confirmation for its details of parameters could be reached from reliable sources.

